text: Harry Rouse (born 20 October 1993) is an English cricketer. He is a right- handed batsman and a right-arm fast medium bowler and has represented Leeds/Bradford MCC University in first-class cricket. He made his first-class debut for Leeds/Bradford MCCU against Yorkshire on 5 April 2013. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Leeds/Bradford MCCU cricketers
